Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.63,0:00:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.64,0:00:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:01:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燃烧不尽的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要把一切毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，我不会逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的背后有卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.59,0:01:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是…\N这时代不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.07,0:01:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十六话\N[燃烧不尽的流星]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲入大气层的运输机接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人的目标明显是这基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是传闻中的新型机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是MD吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以要催毁这基地来说\N数目非常少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们不可以输啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为[特列斯派]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新星作战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是罗姆斐拉财团完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙的MD生产线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.15,0:02:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它们降下地球的作战名称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.09,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了得到地球上的整体权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击有可能反抗的地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,强迫他们归于财团的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在敌人能够使用雷射炮之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽量接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那样才有胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冲过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新星作战\N宇宙好像很喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把麻烦的东西送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了增强兵力支配世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们成功开发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为MD的无人机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，关于使用这些MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其内部有人提出反对意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是OZ统帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对罗姆斐拉财团要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢苟同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老良好传统是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.01,0:04:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的深奥感情构成的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我觉得战斗是美丽的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会申诉生命是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会向逝去的灵魂表示哀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.99,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不须要人类的MD的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自动考虑把OZ解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但想保留现有势力的\N罗姆斐拉财团高层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.03,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想藉着软禁特列斯来镇压事态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那安排现在令支持特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.61,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反对引入MD的OZ士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自称[特列斯派]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗罗姆斐拉财团的支配制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用普通方法果然不能消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受特列斯特校影响的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶的特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增加了多余的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫，继续增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD派落地球的数量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.37,0:05:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你不用担心\N宇宙方面很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新出现的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和驾驶员一起被扣押了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.31,0:05:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会在月面基地消灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹有可能被叛乱份子当作象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要从速解决，兹巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,软禁特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会令时代一直转坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反抗的人就格杀勿论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是最简单和最可靠的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我杀死你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫司令批准\N处决钢弹驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.23,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们再反抗，我们就不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们看来想死在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捕捉了所有目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.92,0:07:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是远远超乎想像的反应速度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提升模拟水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特兰特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络到兹巴洛夫司令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令，这个驾驶舱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来果然装有强化驾驶员脑波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提升战斗能力的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,测试驾驶员显出相等于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的反应速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特兰特\N你听不到我的命令吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫你毁灭钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为蕾蒂‧安的叛变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹的五名技师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在潜伏于这基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别为无聊的事浪费时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这个系统也能用在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.73,0:08:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们OZ的机动战士上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们能使用这部钢弹的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正在消除钢弹这字眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倚靠那种东西做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把钢弹从宇宙的一切记忆里洗掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一切赌在MD身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎办?特兰特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它解体很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但之前，我有数据想记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和MD...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对等战斗的驾驶员的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，脑波没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么检查?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正调查飞翼0的驾驶系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会给予脑波什么影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没问题，那系统很完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团总部的决定而被软禁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的军力现在被一分为二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安中枪倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生死未卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N她被当作背叛罗姆斐拉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧‧麦斯威尔和张五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁OZ内乱成功逃脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两部钢弹的完成度只有80%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，之后只差细微的调较
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两人只要一些时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.46,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能把它们完成吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴顿呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随着拜叶特的爆炸下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生还的可能性非常之低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然不想战斗力下降\N但没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上就是现在的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了吗?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个基地特列斯派的情况吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你们去搜索\N特洛瓦‧巴顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他还可能活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那空域有很多卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他…他一定能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种性格吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为士兵有点问题啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.74,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，虽然拥有那系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但钢弹却落入敌人手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在驾驶舱装有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令战斗的精神波增幅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.38,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能令驾驶员发挥数倍能力的装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对OZ有敌对心是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但驾驶员今次的目的有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为作为士兵还不够完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以它的能力引致自相残杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特和麦丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，加上那部钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能一次催毁月面基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们的运动能力和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战术上的想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,透过训练已经达至完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，士兵的精神方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们相信还不够完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此才引致今次这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们要成为完美的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不能活过MD的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类疯了也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于飞翼0的系统你知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部份早已完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只顾着建造大型能源炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连驾驶舱系统也没注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源炮还未收回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主要的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩光剑和肩膀的机关炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你要战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能把它交给敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，在这场战争里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.78,0:12:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪边是朋友?哪边是敌人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要取自己性命的人和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己想打倒的目标就是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，如果自己错了怎办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，我们没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但名为战争的时代\N却有可能变得疯狂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AB区的闸门被发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多士兵正前来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经包围各位的根据地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不会毫不犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不容分说的\N和曾是战友的你们战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不用流无谓的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全被包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是叫我们出去交易吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不能答应\N释放你们所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我能保证你们的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我们先要互相合作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来五位博士也在那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么要求?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你们把钢弹的驾驶员交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想记录那部钢弹的战斗数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他好像发觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对OZ也有魅力的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.86,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法，叫驾驶员投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于五位博士的生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总部的决定毫不留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.57,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我恐怕无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们活到这年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在是死的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们已经有心理准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先作为人质吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早已料到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那种事对希洛不会有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，有什么问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和他们说开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好\N让他和MD的数据战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.02,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常高的水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD以上吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有余力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,输出极限反应速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能战胜MD的系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争竟然不须要人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，战斗的是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类想倚靠机械\N得到战斗的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!错了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部钢弹是错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是非常高的战斗能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敌人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敌人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.15,0:15:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!起动系统没关掉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用MD制止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是!那不是希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的敌人是要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.99,0:16:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有玩弄我的性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是我的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人质不会对他们有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为那替希洛制造了战斗目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.71,0:17:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这宇宙不需要的是OZ和我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那系统会搞乱人类思考的平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想利用那系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战胜MD的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也已经疯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去受死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们输了就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,输给名为战争的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特兰特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络兹巴洛夫司令要求支援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!我怎能报告这次失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉!那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停步!你做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不停下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们也不想死在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会令他停止攻击  什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的力量能催毁这基地的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦也说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士的驾驶员\N也不行失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若只靠排斥别人的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战争绝对不会完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个驾驶舱会提升战斗能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同时，你会有东西失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我因为那个驾驶舱而失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我因为那种无聊的机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而失去了宝贵的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么\N我不想再失去宝贵的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在能清楚看见敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你也要做我的敌人
