Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球很温柔的
